&lt;p>创建loadbalancer类型的service:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>MetalLB概念安装配置和使用</title><link>https://blog.llaoj.cn/posts/2205/metalb/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.llaoj.cn/posts/2205/metalb/</guid><description>&lt;p>
